    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_320_030_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>現在、バンディ将軍率いる部隊は、
東部国境地帯で敵軍と交戦状態に
あります</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Currently, General Bandi's unit
is positioned in the eastern
national border area.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_320_030_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>戦闘が長期化し、物資確保が
困難となり、部隊は
苦境に立たされており……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The war has dragged on, which has forced
the military to attack neighboring countries
for basic supplies.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271828</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_320_030_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……くそっ……
何やってんだよ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Crap...! What is this!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271828</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_320_030_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんな連中、
オレがいれば、
全滅させてやるのに……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If I was enlisted in the army, I would
have killed them all already...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271996</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_320_030_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>１３歳の時、
オレは軍人になろうと決めた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>When I turned 13, I became a soldier.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271996</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_320_030_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>両親の仇を討ちたかった。
オレにはその選択しかなかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I had to avenge my parents.
It was my only choice.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>TL check</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_320_030_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、全部、
戦争のせいにすんだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So you're going to blame
it on the war, huh?</EnglishText>
      <Notes>TL check</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_320_030_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>デリス・カーラーンを
滅ぼしたのも全部</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Derris Kharlan's destruction and everything else.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_320_030_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>戦争がなかったら
オレは軍人には
ならなかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If there wasn't any war, I wouldn't
have needed to become a soldier.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_320_030_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>デリス・カーラーンも
無事だった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Derris Kharlan would have been fine.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_320_030_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえのように
自分の可能性を……
夢を追いかけていたはずだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You are...that dream of
a possibility come true.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>TL check</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272428</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_320_030_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
